{"tid":1794395,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湯漢聖誕賀辭籲政府聽民意　盡速成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-12-23T05:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T05:58:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d356edc47d405c7aa9c12d71a195b5bb2ec5f31f","tid":1794395,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢樞機發表聖誕賀辭，呼籲各方停止暴力，並再次籲請政府聆聽民意，盡速成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n湯漢表示，自6月政府擬修訂《逃犯條例》觸發遊行示威以來，政府與反修例者的意見對立，其他人士亦意見紛紜，導致社會撕裂，令很多市民精神和情緒上深受創傷，呼籲各方停止暴力、靜心反思、謀求以人道方式解決目前僵局，重建社會和諧，並幫助因社運而在身心靈上受到創傷者獲得治癒。湯漢呼籲政府聆聽民意，盡快成立獨立調查委員會，尋找嚴重警民衝突的真相，以重建官民之間的互信，開闢交談與修好的途徑。<br />\n<br />\n湯漢期盼香港持守民主、自由、法治等核心價值，並早日紓緩貧富懸殊現象，化解矛盾，彰顯正義與和平。他又希望家庭和青年，多關懷貧苦及有需要者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499174-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499174-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=afe051ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499174-20191223.htm&h=49d47e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499174-20191223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3867b6bc6c17a858f7a70458543f6b4a9a5f1041","tid":1794395,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aacde453c2b2ca24635bdc46f9f96e200f710f8","tid":1794395,"uid":20170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"湯漢咁藍都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4103ec373685c09f4887c1a527248c5bd6217